	  </ul>

     <h2>Delicous food</h2>
	  <ul>
       <li><b>Born Fried steamed bun:</b>Shengjian mantou, a homegrown dim sum in Shanghai, is said to have a history of more than 100 years. Sheng jian consists of semi-fermented flour wrapped in fresh meat and meat jelly, placed in rows in a pan, doused with cold water several times during the frying process, and finally sprinkled with scallions and sesame seeds.</li>
       <li><b>Small wonton with three delicacies:</b>Shanghai's three Delicacies wonton is also different from wuxi's. Wonton fillings are not made from fresh meat, foreign vegetables or pickled mustard, but pure meat. The so-called three delicacies are all in the soup, the egg, shrimp skin, laver three delicacies of the fresh meat wrapped in thin skin, taste salty and smooth.</li>
